org.luaj.vm2
Class Lua

java.lang.Object
  org.luaj.vm2.Lua
Direct Known Subclasses:
LuaC, Print
public class Lua
extends java.lang.Object

Constants for lua limits and opcodes.

This is a direct translation of C lua distribution header file constants for bytecode creation and processing.
